Colombia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-chien-thang-cua-anh-truoc-colombia.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Anh ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia 4-3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Jordan Pickford</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 120 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Anh vs Colombia v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Anh vs Colombia v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Diem-nhan-Anh-vs-Colombia-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jordan Pickford gi\u00fap Anh v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Everton \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 NHM Tam s\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Carlos Bacca.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJordan Pickford l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb pha c\u1ee9u thua c\u1ee7a David Seaman tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf World Cup 1998.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00fa ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho Eric Dier, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap Anh ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi Everton b\u1ecf ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Jordan Pickford t\u1eeb Sunderland, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 nghi ng\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPickford c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, c\u1ee9 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Mateus Uribe</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mateus Uribe v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay cho Carlos Sanchez \u1edf ph\u00fat 79. Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u00edt \u1ecfi c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa n\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e1c t\u1ea7m xa bu\u1ed9c Jordan Pickford ph\u1ea3i bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mateus Uribe da hong qua da 11m truoc Anh\" title=\"Mateus Uribe \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/uribe.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mateus Uribe \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c sau \u0111\u00f3 Yerry Mina \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1. Trong 30 ph\u00fat c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 Mateus Uribe c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 11m anh l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMateus Uribe \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin \u1edf qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eadp tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang b\u1eadt ra.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m h\u1ecfng \u0103n c\u1ee7a Mateus Uribe khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ea3 k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp cho Colombia l\u00e0 Carlos Bacca g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1eebng&nbsp;kho\u00e1c \u00e1o AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng \u0103n c\u1ee7a Uribe v\u00e0 Bacca khi\u1ebfn Colombia th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Harry Kane</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Kane \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf World Cup 2018. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane tiep tuc ghi ban\" title=\"Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ed9ng, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i l\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp mang v\u1ec1 1 qu\u1ea3 11 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Anh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 6 c\u1ee7a Harry Kane \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 kh\u00f3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi tay ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKane \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 14 b\u00e0n trong 10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Southgate. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong c\u1ea3 8 tr\u1eadn \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Spurs c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Tommy Lawton n\u0103m 1939.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m c\u00e2n n\u00e3o, Kane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Anh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i David Ospina l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Kane \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t khi ch\u1ecdn ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111eo b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Carlos Sanchez</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Carlos Sanchez ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Colombia \u1edf World Cup 2018. Ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n anh nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Carlos Sanchez choi te hai trong tran dau voi Anh\" title=\"Carlos Sanchez ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/sanchez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Carlos Sanchez ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Carlos Sanchez khi\u1ebfn Colombia ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c anh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u00e9o ng\u00e3 Harry Kane trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Carlos Sanchez kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady b\u1edfi \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Harry Kane. Pha va ch\u1ea1m di\u1ec5n ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 v\u1ecb &ldquo;Vua \u00e1o \u0111en&rdquo; ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m 11m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJose Pekerman kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Carlos Sanchez, anh b\u1ecb thay ra \u1edf ph\u00fat 79. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Yerry Mina&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Carlos Sanchez ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Colombia \u1edf World Cup 2018 th\u00ec Yerry Mina l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina ghi ban trong 3 tran lien tiep o World Cup 2018\" title=\"Yerry Mina ghi b\u00e0n trong 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/mina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Yerry Mina ghi b\u00e0n trong 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-anh-vs-colombia-463-190303.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs Colombia</span> v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, trung v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Miroslav Klose ghi 5 b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup 2002. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Mina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Colombia v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf World Cup 2018, Yerry Mina nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca trao th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Raheem Sterling</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raheem Sterling \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling tiep tuc choi mo nhat\" title=\"Sterling ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/sterling.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng Gareth Southgate n\u00ean lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Sterling \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Rashford ho\u1eb7c Vardy, song \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 47 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia, Sterling ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Harry Kane trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa anh l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Sterling ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t trong th\u1eddi gian xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ra h\u1ed3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSouthgate \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat Sterling \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Vardy, s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Anh kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Vardy khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Colombia g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Southgate thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 11m may r\u1ee7i. Ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 47 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o Sterling \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"888","checkdouble":"190371"},{"date":"17:04 04/07","title":"M\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00ec tai n\u1ea1n, C\u0110V Mexico v\u1eabn v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i \u0111au \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Nga xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/mat-ca-gia-dinh-vi-tai-nan-mot-fan-mexico-van-toi-nga-co-vu-dt.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 lu\u1eadt s\u01b0 Gilberto Martinez, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t fan c\u1ee7a \u0110T Mexico \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u 2 th\u00e1ng.\r\n</h2><h2>V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i \u0111au \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Nga<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t C\u0110V cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao vua, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 41 tu\u1ed5i Gilberto Martinez \u2013 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1edbi Nga c\u1ed5 v\u0169 World Cup c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t tai n\u1ea1n th\u1ea3m kh\u1ed1c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 4 \u0111\u00e3 c\u01b0\u1edbp \u0111i c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1ee3 Veronica c\u00f9ng 2 con, Diego 8 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 Mia 6 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn sau m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, lu\u1eadt s\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1edbi Nga c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh, C\u0110V Gilberto Martinez v\u1eabn t\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0110T h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh, C\u0110V Gilberto Martinez v\u1eabn t\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0110T h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Gilberto-Martinez-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V Gilberto Martinez c\u1ee7a \u0110T Mexico, tr\u00ean tay 2 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o ghi t\u00ean 2 \u0111\u1ee9a con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, Gilberto Martinez v\u1eabn tham d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh. Tr\u00ea h\u00e0nh trang mang \u0111i, anh \u0111em theo 4 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb (ID Fan) t\u1edbi Nga, c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng 3 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 ngay trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u0110T qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Mexico \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch, khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, C\u0110V n\u00e0y nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t tin nh\u1eafn t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Guillermo Ochoa v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p: \u201cChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y d\u00e0nh cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh anh. C\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n d\u1eabn l\u1ed1i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a anh Gilberto Martinez trong \u0111o\u1ea1n clip d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/4/mex.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\">Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean t\u1eeb b\u1ecf nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ngh\u1ec1 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-che-duoc-ronaldo-va-messi-ru-ve-nuoc-neymar-mim-cuoi-noi-khong-421-190277.html\">\u1ea2nh ch\u1ebf: \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi r\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, Neymar m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-nu-cdv-bong-da-quyen-ru-nhat-tai-world-cup-2018-421-189852.html\">Nh\u1eefng n\u1eef C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuoi-dau-ruot-voi-hang-loat-anh-che-ve-that-bai-cua-dt-duc-421-189850.html\">C\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/giup-thoat-hiem-o-vong-bang-nguoi-han-duoc-cdv-mexico-xung-thanh-421-189838.html\">Gi\u00fap tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c C\u0110V Mexico\u2026 x\u01b0ng th\u00e1nh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hy-huu-mot-cdv-anh-lan-loi-ngan-dam-toi-nga-va-phat-hien-quen-ve-o-nha-421-189506.html\">Hy h\u1eefu: M\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh l\u1eb7n l\u1ed9i ng\u00e0n d\u1eb7m t\u1edbi Nga v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n\u2026 qu\u00ean v\u00e9 \u1edf nh\u00e0</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"887","checkdouble":"190373"},{"date":"17:20 04/07","title":"X\u00f3t xa v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u201cso\u00e1i ca\u201d James Rodriguez b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c sao tr\u1eadn thua tuy\u1ec3n Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/xot-xa-voi-hinh-anh-soai-ca-james-rodriguez-bat-khoc-sao-tran-thua-tuyen-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh James Rodriguez trong tr\u1eadn thua \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng.</h2><h2>X\u00f3t xa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh James Rodriguez<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t \u0110T Colombia v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i hoa James Rodriguez kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Colombia, nh\u01b0ng xem ra n\u00f3 ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec so v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i \u0111au c\u1ee7a James &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Senegal, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Bayern Munich ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0110T Colombia. Anh lu\u00f4n s\u00e1t theo m\u1ecdi pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, v\u1ee1 \u00f2a khi trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i khi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c xu\u1ed1ng \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u00ecnh anh ng\u1ed3i \u1edf b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Colombia v\u00ec qu\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a James Rodriguez d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez trong tr\u1eadn thua \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"X\u00f3t xa v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh James Rodriguez trong tr\u1eadn thua \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/james-(2).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>James Rodriguez d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez trong tr\u1eadn thua \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"James\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/081832-10.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0102n m\u1eebng cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez trong tr\u1eadn thua \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"James l\u1ee7i th\u1ee7i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf sau tr\u1eadn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/james.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>James l\u1ee7i th\u1ee7i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf sau tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez trong tr\u1eadn thua \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"James v\u00e0 Henderson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/ja.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Henderson \u0111\u1ebfn chia s\u1ebb c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez trong tr\u1eadn thua \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"James\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/jame.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u00f3t xa v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh James Rodriguez trong tr\u1eadn thua \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/falcao-cay-cu-anh-chien-thang-vi-trong-tai-421-190363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/falcao-cay-cu-anh-chien-thang-vi-trong-tai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/falcao-cay-cu-anh-chien-thang-vi-trong-tai-421-190363.html\">Falcao cay c\u00fa: Anh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00ec tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</span><br>\r\nRadamel Falcao ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Monaco kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 ph\u1ea3i nh