0e0o Raheem Sterling","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/4/dt-anh-southgate-va-niem-tin-mu-quang-vao-raheem-sterling.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Raheem Sterling g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb HLV Gareth Southgate.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raheem Sterling g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Anh v\u00e0 Colombia b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng G.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Raheem Sterling g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00f9 qu\u00e1ng t\u1eeb Southgate h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Raheem Sterling g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00f9 qu\u00e1ng t\u1eeb Southgate h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/sterling.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2, Raheem Sterling \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Harry Kane. Hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 linh h\u1ed3n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Anh, ng\u00f4i sao kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham ch\u01a1i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 1 qu\u1ea3 11m v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ngo\u00e0i ra Harry Kane c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a HLV Southgate v\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 (6 b\u00e0n). Kane \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 14 b\u00e0n trong 10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Southgate. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong c\u1ea3 8 tr\u1eadn \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Spurs c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Tommy Lawton n\u0103m 1939.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Kane g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn th\u00ec Raheem Sterling ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City ch\u01a1i v\u1eadt v\u1edd trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Sterling ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 35 l\u1ea7n, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Anh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 3 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling Colombia vs Anh\" title=\"Sterling Colombia vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Du-am-Colombia-vs-Anh-Pha-loi-nguyen-11m-va-sang-trang-lich-su-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Vardy \u1edf ph\u00fat 88. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-chien-thang-cua-anh-truoc-colombia-421-190371.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Lingard l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0110T Anh</span> \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Sterling g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 quen thu\u1ed9c, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia, Sterling kh\u00f4ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Panama anh c\u00f3 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Sterling \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh 3 trong 4 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 tung ra 5 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man City v\u1edbi 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Sterling \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sterling x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate v\u00e0o Sterling \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 47 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Jamie Vardy v\u00e0 Marcus Rashford x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh h\u01a1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling xung dang ngoi du bi cho Vardy hoac Rashford\" title=\"Sterling x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Vardy ho\u1eb7c Rashford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/vardy.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Vardy ho\u1eb7c Rashford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia, Vardy v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111e d\u1ecda khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. Vardy ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Sterling.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Southgate kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Vardy, \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Rashford, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea khi\u1ebfn Southgate c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Sterling v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Vardy ho\u1eb7c Rashford: Sterling \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 t\u1edbi 12 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n \u1edf&nbsp;Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Rashford v\u00e0 Vardy ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVardy v\u00e0 Rashford s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Sterling. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng gi\u00fap anh ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i t\u00f3m l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i Sterling kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Southgate ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00f9 qu\u00e1ng v\u00e0o ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Tam s\u01b0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"885","checkdouble":"190376"},{"date":"09:40 04/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/nhung-thong-tin-thu-vi-ve-cac-doi-gop-mat-tai-tu-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 n\u01a1i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi 6/14 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n (chi\u1ebfm t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 42.85%), Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 2/5 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n (40%), ch\u00e2u \u00c1, ch\u00e2u Phi v\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c B\u1eafc - Trung M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00e0o.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng tin th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Thong-tin-thu-vi-ve-cac-doi-gop-mat-tai-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n* Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup (t\u00ednh t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Li\u00ean X\u00f4 tan r\u00e3).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng A (Nga, Uruguay) v\u00e0 G (Anh, B\u1ec9) sau khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. B\u1ea3ng B v\u00e0 H kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1eb7p Uruguay, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina (4-3, v\u00f2ng 1/8) v\u00e0 Peru (1-0, v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* T\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u00ednh sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 Uruguay v\u00e0 B\u1ec9, Croatia to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110an M\u1ea1ch tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Uruguay\" title=\"Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/da-bai-bo-dao-nha-hlv-uruguay-no-tung-bung.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Uruguay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u00ednh trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n* Trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Brazil (5), Uruguay (2), Anh v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p (1) l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 Brazil v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2002.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u00e0 Brazil (Nam M\u1ef9), B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n duy nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1eeb c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c kh\u00e1c nhau g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, g\u1ed3m Anh (ch\u00e2u \u00c2u), Panama (B\u1eafc - Trung M\u1ef9), Tunisia (ch\u00e2u Phi) v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (ch\u00e2u \u00c1).<br />\r\n<p>* N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh theo ph\u00e2n nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eb1m trong  nh\u00f3m 1 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1ed3m Nga (ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0), Brazil, Ph\u00e1p, B\u1ec9, 3 \u0111\u1ed9i thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m 2  g\u1ed3m Anh, Croatia v\u00e0 Uruguay, nh\u00f3m 3 ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n duy nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y  \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi dung do Brazil o tu ket\" title=\"B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/191516-bi.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ec9 \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eafm gi\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>* B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World  Cup 2018 (12 - \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i), Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t (6 - \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 9 t\u1ea1i  gi\u1ea3i).</p>\r\n<p>* Trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Nga c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh cao nh\u1ea5t (28.8),  sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 Brazil (28.6), Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Uruguay (28.1), Croatia (27.9), B\u1ec9  (27.6), Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Anh (26).</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-tu-ket-world-cup-2018-nhung-thong-tin-can-biet-465-190344.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/lich-thi-dau-tu-ket-world-cup-2018-nhung-thong-tin-can-biet.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-tu-ket-world-cup-2018-nhung-thong-tin-can-biet-465-190344.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft</span><br />\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup 2018 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"884","checkdouble":"190347"},{"date":"09:39 04/07","title":"C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng g\u1ecdi t\u00ean ai?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/golden-boot-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 World Cup, ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ebd trao nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 5 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng sau gi\u1ea3i, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng hay th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1982. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Paolo Rossi v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u0169ng trong n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, Rossi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Italia gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/golden-boot-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao d\u1ef1a theo y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n, c\u00e1c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n1. Ai ghi b\u0